atus%2F1241692166247854085%3Fs%3D21&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdKHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=970a2a0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmel_faith1%2Fstatus%2F1241692166247854085%3Fs%3D21&h=71263b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mel_faith1/status/1241692166247854085?s=21</a><br />\n係講個係美國住嘅女仔為左Chinese身分道歉，佢移左民，但佢都好醒目，知道所有黃種人樣嘅人係外國通常都會被統稱為&rdquo;Chinese&rdquo;，而一個黃種人單方而否認I am not Chinese 其實鬼佬心底都會係當你Chinese，最少打你果時會<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/22/210645_6fdc37d92a56069e6f2c91abd8007a31.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2F210645_6fdc37d92a56069e6f2c91abd8007a31.jpeg&h=bef62e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/22/210828_09ebf2e603a59702f6ac316fe41f85b1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2F210828_09ebf2e603a59702f6ac316fe41f85b1.jpeg&h=deb106ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n縱觀個反應幾好<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/329qsZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F329qsZA.jpg&h=4c353b75&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/22/211039_615da20614af4ad081c9ed2f2d7a15da.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F22%2F211039_615da20614af4ad081c9ed2f2d7a15da.jpeg&h=5782bffa&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPXrWUX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPXrWUX.jpg&h=fcf59861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n其實當年納粹德軍都殺左好多人<br />\n但佢勝在肯道歉認錯<br />\nD人反而會同情翻果d唔關事嘅後人<br />\n從而變成正單一針對個政權<br />\n<br />\nDale Carnegie講過個例子<br />\n如果一個人遲到，之後佢仲賴呢樣賴果樣會令到人更加反感eg.最衰塞車，唔係我唔會遲<br />\n反而係直接話：係我錯，我唔應該遲到，我應該早d出門，塞車唔係藉口，係我自己無做好充份準備，最衰都係我，我明知工作緊要但仲遲到係不知所謂，我下次會改<br />\n咁樣對方最少條氣順左，反而無咁會為難你，倒頭好多時仲會幫你講好說話<br />\n<br />\n今次